Eleanor Hartley 提出视觉的通透感是这类结构重要的美学特征.<ref>Eleanor Hartley, "Ken Snelson and the Aesthetics of Structure," in the Marlborough Gallery catalogue for ''Kenneth Snelson: Selected Work: 1948 - 2009'', exhibited February 19 through March 21, 2009.</ref> Korkmaz ''et al.''<ref name="korkmaz">Korkmaz, et al. (June 2011)</ref> 将张拉整体的结构概念拓展应用于自适应建筑，主要应用了其轻质的特性。

